md:
giải nghĩa từ "partial" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.

* Partial (adjective)
	+ Meaning: Not complete or total; not fully developed or formed.
	+ Vietnamese: Không đầy đủ; không hoàn toàn.
	+ Example: The partial eclipse of the sun was visible from our location.
	+ Related words: incomplete, imperfect, unfinished.

* Partial (adjective)
	+ Meaning: Favouring one person or group over another; biased.
	+ Vietnamese: Có thiên vị; không công bằng.
	+ Example: The judge was accused of being partial towards the defendant.
	+ Related words: biased, unfair, discriminatory.

* Partial (noun)
	+ Meaning: A part of something; a portion.
	+ Vietnamese: Một phần; một bộ phận.
	+ Example: The partial remains of the ancient city were discovered by archaeologists.
	+ Related words: part, portion, fragment.

Note: The meanings of "partial" can vary depending on the context in which it is used.
